ures, coma, respiratory arrest, and death.', 'Synergism', 'Caution is advised when vasopressin or desmopressin is used in combination with drugs that can cause fluid retention or SIADH.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/98592/', '', 'Terlipressin, Oxytocin', 'Felodipine, Amlodipine, Moexipril, Verapamil, Ramipril, Lisinopril, Perindopril, Bisoprolol, Benazepril, Quinapril, Trandolapril, More', 1767369485);
